@page "/sanity-publisher"

<PageTitle>Sanity Publisher</PageTitle>

<h1>Sanity Publisher</h1>

<p class="lead">
    Publish approved articles into Sanity.io with title, slug, configured author,
    main image, categories, markdown/rich text body, CJ ads, and SEO fields.
</p>

<div class="workspace-card">
    <h2>Publishing Workflow</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Select approved article draft.</li>
        <li>Select CJ ads to sprinkle into the article.</li>
        <li>Generate article hero image prompt.</li>
        <li>Send article fields to Sanity.</li>
        <li>Publish article.</li>
        <li>Email live article link.</li>
        <li>Generate social post drafts.</li>
    </ol>
</div>
